## PATTERN 3: BOXED LUNCHES (Separate System)

Boxed lunches use their own tables (NOT shadow menu, NOT stations):
- `Boxed Lunch Orders` (`tbldRHfhjCY4x2Hyy`)
- `Boxed Lunch Order Items` (`tblbkSAnNpUkjWtsa`)
- `Box Customizations` (`tblAulNkoIFgNhJxw`)

V2 payload stores JSON in the `orderName` field with prefix `FWX_BOXED_V2:`.

Sandwich choices come from `fetchMenuItemsByBoxLunchType()` which queries Menu Items by `Box Lunch Type` field.

### Files
- `src/config/boxedLunchBeo.ts` — box types, sandwich suggestions
- `src/services/airtable/boxedLunchOrders.ts` — load/save orders
- `src/components/beo-intake/BoxedLunchSection.tsx` — intake UI
- `src/utils/boxedLunchPrint.ts` — BEO print rendering

