## PATTERN 4: SANDWICH PLATTERS (LocalStorage)

Sandwich platters use `localStorage` (NOT Airtable):
- Config in `src/config/sandwichPlatterConfig.ts` — PLATTER_CHOICES defines types, options, maxPick
- State in `src/state/platterOrdersStore.ts`
- UI in `src/components/beo-intake/SandwichPlatterConfigModal.tsx`

To add a new platter type, add it to `PLATTER_CHOICES` with options and maxPick.

