## CURRENT GAP ANALYSIS (April 2026)

### Full-Service Intake — Picker Issues

The full-service pickers (Passed Apps, Presented Apps, Buffet Metal, Buffet China, Desserts, Stations) work differently depending on which table is configured:

**When `.env` points to Menu_Lab (`tbl6gXRT2FPpTdf0J`):**
- Pickers use `Display Type` field to filter
- BUT Menu_Lab only has these Display Type values: `BUFFET` (85), `DISPLAY` (43), `COLD DISPLAY` (13)
- The picker code expects: `PASSED APPETIZERS`, `PRESENTED APPETIZERS`, `BUFFET METAL`, `BUFFET CHINA`, `DESSERTS`, `STATION`
- **Result: ALL full-service pickers show 0 items from Menu_Lab**

**When `.env` points to Legacy (`tbl0aN33DGG6R1sPZ`):**
- Pickers use `Category` field (single select)
- Legacy has: `Passed App` (17), `Presented App` (30), `Buffet Metal` (3), `Buffet` (41), `Dessert` (42), `Station Item` (39)
- These match the legacy picker formula patterns
- **Full-service works correctly with legacy table**

### To fix full-service pickers with Menu_Lab:

**Option A (Recommended — fastest):** Add the missing Display Type values to Menu_Lab records. Bulk-update records to add tags like `PASSED APPETIZERS`, `PRESENTED APPETIZERS`, `BUFFET METAL`, `BUFFET CHINA`, `DESSERTS`, `STATION` to the Display Type multi-select field. Use the legacy Category as a guide for which tag each item should get.

**Option B:** Modify the picker code in `menuCatalogConfig.ts` to map existing Menu_Lab Display Type values to the picker categories. E.g., map `BUFFET` → `buffet_metal`, `DISPLAY` → `presented`, etc. Risk: too coarse — one `BUFFET` tag covers items that should be in different sections.

### Legacy Table Category → Menu_Lab Display Type mapping guide:

| Legacy Category | Should get Display Type | Notes |
|----------------|------------------------|-------|
| Passed App | PASSED APPETIZERS | 17 items |
| Presented App | PRESENTED APPETIZERS | 30 items |
| Buffet Metal | BUFFET METAL | 3 items (need more) |
| Buffet, Buffet Item, Entrée, Protein, Pasta, Vegetable, Starch | BUFFET METAL or BUFFET CHINA | Need to sort by hot vs cold |
| Dessert, Dessert (Individual), Dessert (Display) | DESSERTS | 54 items total |
| Station Item | STATION | 39 items |
| Deli, Deli/Sandwhiches | Already handled by delivery intake | |
| Component | Child items — no Display Type needed | |

